msgstr "On iOS, an explicit Close button is required (swipe down does not work). Android also dismisses on back navigation."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal.tsx:33
msgid "iOS では「閉じる」ボタンが必須（swipe down 不可）。Android では戻る操作でも閉じる。"
