#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/card.tsx:22
msgid "OS / テーマに応じたスライドアニメーションで push される。システムの戻るボタン / ジェスチャーで戻れる。"
msgstr "Pushed with an OS/theme-driven slide animation. Dismissed via the system back button or gesture."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/modal.tsx:21
msgid "presentation 形式は modal になるが、画面遷移アニメーションは独立した `animation` プロパティで決まる。`animation` 未指定だと `card` と同じ OS 標準の遷移 (多くは右からスライド) になり、iOS のような「下から上」にはならない。下から上にしたい場合は `animation: slide_from_bottom` を明示する。戻るボタン / システムジェスチャーで閉じられる。"
msgstr "The presentation style becomes `modal`, but the transition animation is controlled separately by the `animation` prop. With `animation` unspecified, it uses the OS-default transition (often slide-in from the right, same as `card`), not the iOS-style \"slide up from the bottom\". Set `animation: slide_from_bottom` explicitly to slide up. Dismissed via the back button or system gesture."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal.tsx:14
msgid "swipe で閉じられない全画面モーダル"
msgstr "Full-screen modal that cannot be dismissed by swipe"

#: src/app/(tabs)/(home)/navigation-patterns/index.tsx:18
#: src/app/navigation-patterns/transparent-modal.tsx:11
msgid "transparentModal"
msgstr "transparentModal"

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/contained-modal.tsx:16
msgid "UIModalPresentationCurrentContext で表示される。`definesPresentationContext: true` を持つ最も近い祖先 view controller の bounds 内に重なる。タブ内側 Stack で開けばタブバーが残る。`fullScreenModal` との差は表示範囲で、`fullScreenModal` は presentation context に関係なく画面全体を覆うが、`containedModal` は presentation context の bounds 内に収まる。swipe down では閉じない (UIKit の `UIModalPresentationCurrentContext` 自体が sheet ジェスチャーを持たないため)。ただしこれは React Navigation 公式が明示的に保証している挙動ではない点に注意。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationCurrentContext. Overlays within the bounds of the closest ancestor view controller that has `definesPresentationContext: true`. When opened from an in-tab Stack, the tab bar remains visible. The difference from `fullScreenModal` is the display area: `fullScreenModal` covers the entire screen regardless of presentation context, while `containedModal` stays within the bounds of the presentation context. Swipe down does not dismiss it (because UIKit's `UIModalPresentationCurrentContext` itself does not provide a sheet gesture). Note however that this behavior is not explicitly guaranteed by React Navigation."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/form-sheet.tsx:16
msgid "UIModalPresentationFormSheet で表示される。detent (snap point) を任意の数だけ指定可。sheetGrabberVisible で上端のつまみを表示できる。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationFormSheet. Any number of detents (snap points) can be configured. `sheetGrabberVisible` shows the grabber at the top."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/full-screen-modal.tsx:16
msgid "UIModalPresentationFullScreen で画面全体を覆う。`containedModal` が presentation context の bounds 内に収まるのに対し、`fullScreenModal` は presentation context に関係なく画面全体を覆う。React Navigation 公式に「ジェスチャーで dismiss できない」と明記されているため (`A screen using this presentation style cannot be dismissed by gesture.`)、swipe で閉じない挙動はライブラリの保証として依拠できる。明示的な閉じる操作が必須。"
msgstr "Covers the entire screen with UIModalPresentationFullScreen. While `containedModal` stays within the bounds of the presentation context, `fullScreenModal` covers the entire screen regardless of presentation context. React Navigation officially documents that `A screen using this presentation style cannot be dismissed by gesture.`, so its no-swipe-dismiss behavior can be relied on as a library guarantee. An explicit dismiss action is required."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/contained-transparent-modal.tsx:17
msgid "UIModalPresentationOverCurrentContext で表示される。透過を保ったまま current context の上に重なる。"
msgstr "Presented with UIModalPresentationOverCurrentContext. Layered on top of the current context while remaining transparent."

#: src/app/navigation-patterns/form-sheet.tsx:14
msgid "シート表示（detent 対応）"
msgstr "Sheet presentation with detent support"

